there are two kinds of hatred.

54:47.680 --> 54:50.647
The feeling we simply call...

54:50.680 --> 54:51.847
hatred...

54:51.881 --> 54:56.047
which is related to things
that are bad for the soul.

54:56.714 --> 55:00.847
The other is the feeling
called, horreur!

55:00.881 --> 55:05.181
Which is related to things
that are ugly for the soul.

55:11.114 --> 55:13.347
Then I hate my mother...

55:16.313 --> 55:18.647
