57:21.480 --> 57:23.547
a tiny gland,

57:23.580 --> 57:26.180
no bigger than a pine nut,

57:26.213 --> 57:31.280
that is the meeting place,
of body and mind.

57:33.380 --> 57:36.113
I am convinced,

57:36.146 --> 57:41.714
this, is where
our emotions are born.

57:41.747 --> 57:43.580
